{"tid":1817430,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【咁撚夠疆？？】內地專家指武漢不明肺炎疫情人傳人可能性很大","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T05:43:53.000Z","uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa20270887e6ba944c857f7c78629418e65445f3","tid":1817430,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"內地初步判定，武漢的不明原因肺炎個案為新型冠狀病毒。北京大學醫學部基礎醫學院免疫學系教授王月丹認為，今次疫情人傳人的可能性很大，根據2003年沙士經驗，冠狀病毒在人與人之間會傳播，因此需要弄清楚傳播途徑以及是透過那些媒介傳播，再採取相應措施，同時監察疫情，每天公布有否新增病例，消除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n王月丹說，不能夠排除其他省市會有病例，內地各出入境口岸要加強檢疫。他表示，雖然暫時不能夠判斷今次的疫情源於野味，但認同要停售野生動物，民眾亦要避免到人多的地方及不要接觸發燒的病人。<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501835-20200109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501835-20200109.htm&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF03XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=85aa54e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501835-20200109.htm&h=9eaec189\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501835-20200109.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552e52e495e305373fd40dac1746c6f44cfa265c","tid":1817430,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"重演03年攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}